polaris_dvc
Copyright 2026 Polaris DVC Contributors

This product is a Rust re-implementation inspired by:

  DVC (HWPX Document Validation Checker)
  Copyright (c) 2022 Hancom Inc.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
  https://github.com/hancom-io/dvc

Rule JSON schema, JID (error-code) constants, and the output JSON field
layout are designed to remain compatible with the upstream DVC project so
existing DVC assets (rule files, tooling) can be reused unchanged.

A snapshot of the upstream DVC source used for reference is retained in
`third_party/dvc-upstream/` for traceability. No compiled code from that
snapshot is distributed as part of this project.
